# 🔹 Most Important GATE Traps

### Trap 1

BST Search:

Not always O(log n)

Worst case:

[
O(n)
]

---

### Trap 2

Hashing:

Not always O(1)

Worst case:

[
O(n)
]

---

### Trap 3

Heap Search:

[
O(n)
]

NOT O(log n)

---

### Trap 4

Build Heap:

[
O(n)
]

NOT O(nlogn)

---

### Trap 5

BFS and DFS:

[
O(V+E)
]

NOT O(V²)

(for adjacency list)

